Original vintage image designed to look like an antique sign. The image is printed directly to a distressed wood panel made from 1/2 inch tongue and groove slats. Often the wood will have minor imperfections and other natural characteristics of real wood. There could be slight cracks where the slats come together. Any of the text on our signs can be customized. All of our images have the look and feel of real vintage signs. They can hang outside as long as they are in a sheltered area.

Suzanne Nicoll Holiday image printed directly to a distressed wood panel made from tongue and groove slats of alder, hemlock, or fir lumber. The panel is 15"x 26" or 20"x32" and 1" thick and has knots and other natural irregularities making each piece of art appear to be a vintage antique. The image is fade resistant and will last many years. For indoor use or outside in a covered area. Made in the USA
